snippet.title: [Level 1 Stats] Valkyria Chronicles 3 E2 - Extra Missions: Liberate the Aqueduct - 1 Turn
snippet.description:
Mission Name: Liberate the Aqueduct
Mission Objectives: Defeat Heavy Tank CO.
Restrictions: None
Grade: ★★★★★
Ace Name: Yoshino the Bewitching
Ace Drop 1: Helmwige
Ace Drop 2: None
Ranking: S: 4 | A: 5 | B: 6 | C: 20

This is a DLC mission that is not included in the "E2" version of Valkyria Chronicles 3 and therefore, entirely in Japanese. Translations may not be 100% accurate but it is at least something to go off.
